'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2550] on 1 September 2000 at 7:52:32 am'!"Change Set:		miscFixesDate:			31 August 2000Author:			Bob Arning- initialize EToySenderMorph with user's name and IP address when taken from new morph menu- fixed walkback when deleting ProjectNavigationMorph from the control menu"!!EToySenderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 8/31/2000 18:32'!initialize	Socket initializeNetwork.				"we may want our IP address"	Preferences defaultAuthorName.		"seems like a good place to insure we have a name"	super initialize.	orientation _ #vertical.	color _ Color lightMagenta.	inset _ 4.	borderColor _ Color magenta.	borderWidth _ 4.	self setProperty: #normalBorderColor toValue: borderColor.	self setProperty: #flashingColors toValue: {Color red. Color yellow}.! !!EToySenderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 8/31/2000 18:31'!installModelIn: myWorld	"if we get this far and nothing exists, make it up"	userPicture ifNotNil: [^self].	self		userName: Preferences defaultAuthorName 		userPicture: nil 		userEmail: 'who@where.net' 		userIPAddress: NetNameResolver localAddressString! !!ProjectNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 9/1/2000 07:51'!mouseLeave: evt	self world ifNil: [^self].		"can happen after delete from control menu"	(self worldBounds containsPoint: evt cursorPoint) ifFalse: [^self].	mouseInside _ false.	self positionVertically.! !